title: Pop Culture Trivia War & Friendship With Shane Is Over - Frenemies #18
description: On this episode of Frenemies Ethan & Trish have a battle of wits as we finally get to our pop culture trivia competition (with grilled cheese, of course). We also talk a bit about Shane & Rylan's snakeishness, and Trisha's new music video!
